10:18.535 --> 10:20.245
<i>I'm running out of time.</i>

10:20.245 --> 10:23.123
I'm not really sure
I can get everything done.

10:23.123 --> 10:25.458
<i>[hard rock music]</i>

10:25.458 --> 10:27.669
- I'm going to the grinder
to shape my blade.

10:27.669 --> 10:29.921
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:29.921 --> 10:33.424
When I'm grinding off,
I'm seeing inclusions.

10:33.424 --> 10:35.635
These may not be cracks.

10:35.635 --> 10:38.555
<i>These could just be the way</i>
<i>that the steel is forming.</i>

10:38.555 --> 10:40.515
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:40.515 --> 10:41.683
It's now back to the forge.

10:41.683 --> 10:44.144
We got to harden this puppy.

10:44.144 --> 10:46.479
- Sam looks like he's setting
up for an edge quench.

10:46.479 --> 10:48.273
