11:18.261 --> 11:20.221
We're at the end.
It's done.

11:20.221 --> 11:23.808
<i>[hard rock music]</i>

11:23.808 --> 11:26.728
- DJ had a lot of problems
getting his steel together.

11:26.728 --> 11:28.479
How does it look, Doug?

11:28.479 --> 11:30.565
- From the looks of it,
it looks like a solid piece.

11:30.565 --> 11:33.026
- I know the blade is starting
to look like a blade now,

11:33.026 --> 11:35.278
so I'm getting ready
for the heat treat.

11:35.278 --> 11:37.030
<i>If you do it too hot,</i>

